This directory contains bluetooth driver layer code.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
It provide bluetooth driver interfaces for stack.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================

It needs the following libs from AOSP:
1.  libdl.so

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1. liblog.so

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.


HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Files in this directory is used to
generate a library which's name is 'libbluetoothdrv.so'


All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..

